description:
#### 1.0.1: Twitter updates and Fixed the bugs ####

About

* WikiLeaks is an international organization that publishes submissions of private, secret, and classified media from anonymous news sources and news leaks.

* Are you missed the documents or finding those secret news are very difficult. By using this app you can do very easily.

* The first Wiki Leaks application is now available in palm.

* Now you can easily search 2+ Lacks of documents.

* This app is very fast, and accurate.

* You can also share your search result to yours friends.

Features:
* Easy way to search all Wiki Leaks document information.

* Easy navigation's are possible.

* Share your important information to your family members or dearest ones or friends.

* Attractive User Interface & easy to use!

* Support wikiLeaks for better world.
